      <title>PNC 净利息收入低于预期，贷款增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/pnc-net-interest-income-misses-estimates-with-loan-growth-muted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PNC Financial Services Group Inc. 第一季度净利息收入未达到预期，这表明这家总部位于匹兹堡的银行继续因贷款增长放缓而苦苦挣扎。]]></description>
